These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, metal, techno, country
There are 4 different favourite colors: coral, turquise, aquamarine, black
1. the fan of metal is somewhere to the right of the fan of hip-hop##5
2. the person who likes black is on the left or right of the person who likes coral##3
3. the person who likes coral is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of country is somewhere to the left of the person who likes black##5
5. the person who likes coral is the fan of metal##1
6. the fan of techno is the person who likes turquise##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre      | country  | hip-hop | metal  | techno |
| Color   | aquamarine | black      | coral | turquise |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, photography, board-games, camping
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: dahlia, poppy, marigold, lily
1. the person who's hobby is photography is between the person who growsdahlia and the person who growslily##2
2. the person who's hobby is camping is somewhere to the left of the person who growslily##5
3. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
4. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
5. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby   | camping | board-games | photography   | cooking |
| Flower           | marigold      | dahlia    | poppy | lily      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, hip-hop, reggae, d&b
There are 4 different nationalities: french, chinese, german, colombian
1. the fan of hip-hop is the chinese##1
2. the colombian is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
3. the german is somewhere to the left of the french##5
4. the french is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
5. the fan of d&b is somewhere to the right of the colombian##5
6. the fan of hip-hop is somewhere to the left of the german##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre        | hip-hop | classical | reggae     | d&b |
| Nationality   | chinese  | colombian   | german | french    |

