.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-4::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, metal, house, techno
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, iced-tea, 7up, hot-chocolate
1. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of metal##1
2. the fan of techno is somewhere to the right of the person drinking 7up##5
3. the fan of hip-hop is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person drinking iced-tea##2
4. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the fan of house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |      4      |
| Music-Genre         | house | hip-hop | metal | techno |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate   | 7up     | iced-tea    | sprite       |

