.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-5::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, sunflower, lily, zinnia
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, december, november, july
1. the person who growszinnia is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in june##5
2. the person who growszinnia is on the left or right of the person who growslily##3
3. the person who growslily is somewhere to the left of the person who growsamaryllis##5
4. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
5. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the person who growssunflower##3
6. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |    3     |    4    |
| Flower          | lily | zinnia   | amaryllis   | sunflower    |
| Birthday   | december  | july | june | november |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-6::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, brown, lavender, black
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, january, april, december
1. the person who likes black is in an odd position##4
2. the person who likes blood-red is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in december##5
3. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person who likes black and the person who's birthday is in april##2
4. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |       3        |     4     |
| Color           | blood-red | brown | black | lavender |
| Birthday   | april        | december     | july       | january   |

