.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-7::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, rugby, cycling, golf
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, 7up, coffee, soy-milk
1. the person drinking 7up is the person who's sport is golf##1
2. the person who's sport is swimming is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person drinking coffee##2
3. the person drinking lemonade is in an even position##4
4. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is swimming##5
5. the person who's sport is swimming is in an even position##4
6. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Sport   | rugby | swimming  | cycling  | golf   |
| Beverage           | soy-milk  | lemonade | coffee | 7up |

