.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-8::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, badminton, golf, ice-hockey
House: craftsman, victorian, colonial, wooden
1. the victorian house is on the right of the wooden house##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is somewhere to the left of the colonial house##5
3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
4. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
5. the colonial house is somewhere to the left of the craftsman house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Sport   | badminton     | ice-hockey | golf     | climbing   |
| House    | wooden | victorian  | colonial | craftsman |

