.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-9::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, ice-hockey, rugby, weightlifting
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, lily, tulip, poppy
1. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
2. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
3. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is somewhere to the right of the person who growspoppy##5
5. the person who growslily is somewhere to the right of the person who growsrose##5
6. the person who growsrose is somewhere to the left of the person who growstulip##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |   3    |  4   |
| Sport   | skiing | rugby | weightlifting   | ice-hockey |
| Flower       | rose       | tulip   | poppy | lily |

