.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-10::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, chaman, blend, siglo
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, jazz, trance, country
1. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the fan of jazz##3
2. the fan of salsa is somewhere to the left of the siglo-smoker##5
3. the fan of country is somewhere to the right of the chaman-smoker##5
4. the fan of salsa is somewhere to the right of the fan of country##5
5. the fan of jazz is somewhere to the left of the cain-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |   3    |     4      |
| Cigar   | chaman | blend       | cain   | siglo        |
| Music-Genre      | jazz  | country | salsa | trance |

