There are 4 different favourite colors: aquamarine, coral, blood-red, lavender
1. the fan of funk is somewhere to the left of the fan of indie##5
2. the person who likes blood-red is the fan of trance##1
3. the person who likes coral is on the left of the fan of indie##1
4. the fan of techno is somewhere to the right of the person who likes blood-red##5
5. the person who likes coral is somewhere to the left of the person who likes aquamarine##5
6. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left or right of the person who likes coral##3
7. the fan of trance is somewhere to the right of the person who likes aquamarine##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | funk | indie   | trance | techno     |
| Color   | coral     | aquamarine | blood-red  | lavender |

