.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-12::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, game, alhambra, havana
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, canadian, german, indonesian
1. the indonesian is on the left of the colombian##1
2. the indonesian is in an even position##4
3. the havana-smoker is somewhere to the left of the canadian##5
4. the vegafina-smoker is the german##1
5. the havana-smoker is somewhere to the right of the alhambra-smoker##5
6. the canadian is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |     3      |  4   |
| Cigar   | vegafina | alhambra        | havana        | game |
| Nationality         | german  | indonesian | colombian | canadian |

