.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-13::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, rose, begonia, zinnia
4 different pets are kept: goat, guinea-pig, snake, pony
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person who growsrose##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goat##5
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is in an odd position##4
4. the person who growsbegonia is somewhere to the left of the owner of the pony##5
5. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
6. the person who growszinnia is the owner of the pony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Flower         | begonia | zinnia | rose | azalea |
| Pet   | goat     | pony  | guinea-pig  | snake    |

