.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-14::.
There 4 different types of food: lettuce, artichoke, lime, corn
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, helicopter, van, scooter
1. the person eating lettuce is somewhere to the right of the person driving the van##5
2. the person eating lime is somewhere to the right of the person driving the boat##5
3. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
4. the person driving the scooter is the person eating lime##1
5. the person eating artichoke is somewhere to the right of the person eating lettuce##5
6. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person driving the boat##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3      |    4     |
| Food   | corn  | lettuce | artichoke | lime |
| Transport   | van | boat | helicopter   | scooter  |

