.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-15::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, tram, snowmobile, helicopter
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, jazz, blues, disco
1. the person driving the helicopter is between the person driving the snowmobile and the person driving the tram##2
2. the fan of country is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
3. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
4. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the right of the fan of blues##5
5. the fan of blues is somewhere to the left of the fan of disco##5
6. the fan of blues is on the left of the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |      3       |     4     |
| Transport   | ship | snowmobile  | helicopter      | tram |
| Music-Genre     | blues    | disco | jazz | country   |

