.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-16::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, azure, mauve, lilac
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, librarian, photographer, videographer
1. the person who likes mauve is in an even position##4
2. the person who likes lilac is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who likes azure is on the right of the videographer##1
4. the bartender is in an even position##4
5. the person who likes brown is somewhere to the left of the person who likes lilac##5
6. the person who likes mauve is between the person who likes brown and the librarian##2
7. the person who likes azure is somewhere to the right of the person who likes brown##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |
| Color      | brown   | mauve  | azure      | lilac       |
| Job   | photographer | videographer | librarian | bartender |

