.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-17::.
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, apple, peach, lime
City: san-francisco, edinburgh, venice, prague
1. the person eating lime is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to prague##5
2. the person eating peach is the person traveling to prague##1
3. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
4. the person eating lime is somewhere to the right of the person eating cauliflower##5
5. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person eating apple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Food   | cauliflower     | apple | lime | peach |
| City     | edinburgh | san-francisco    | venice    | prague |

