2. the person who likes mauve is somewhere to the right of the person who likes ebony##5
3. the person who likes lavender is somewhere to the left of the person who growsdaisy##5
4. the person who likes mauve is somewhere to the left of the person who growspoppy##5
5. the person who likes mauve is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
6. the person who growsdaisy is between the person who growsballoon-flower and the person who likes ivory##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |       4       |
| Flower      | zinnia     | balloon-flower | daisy     | poppy |
| Color   | lavender | ebony  | mauve | ivory        |

