.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-20::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, satire, thriller, action
House: colonial, victorian, craftsman, cape-cod
1. the person watching satire movies is somewhere to the left of the victorian house##5
2. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
3. the craftsman house is in an odd position##4
4. the colonial house is somewhere to the right of the victorian house##5
5. the person watching satire movies is somewhere to the left of the cape-cod house##5
6. the person watching martial-arts movies is between the person watching action movies and the colonial house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre        | satire     | action | martial-arts | thriller |
| House   | craftsman | cape-cod | victorian      | colonial        |

 